title: Byron Cigars
itunes:title: Byron Cigars
description: This week we're smoking some of the best cigars in the world. Push those  Cubans aside and find out what the best of the best truly is.... Today  on The Cigar Authority we're joined by Stephen Adib and Woody Brown from  Selected Tobacco and Cuba Rica. We're smoking the acclaimed Byron,  Atabey, Bandolero, Via Havana and Testarosso.
